                            <comment id="17388665" author="zabetak" created="Wed, 28 Jul 2021 10:13:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=kkasa&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;kkasa&quot;&gt;kkasa&lt;/a&gt;&#160;Do you know if compaction can also affect MERGE statements in a similar fashion?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
